The following code conventions are the preferred stylings for the MUDscape project:

In general, MUDScape will follow PEP8 guidelines to ensure consistently styled code and readability.
Any deviations from PEP8 are listed below:

1. functions are to be written in camelCase(), as opposed to PEP8's lower_case() style
2. line lengths are to be capped at a maximum of 120 characters
3. . . .